OL,12,Ftoo slowly", which resulted in "high   
OL,13,Flevels of estimated fraud", it said.   
OL,15,FIt added the Department for Business   
OL,16,Festimated fraudulent loans were worth  
OL,17,F#4.9bn, 11% of the total, as of March. 
